{"tid":2440510,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保險業：若接種疫苗後離世　不會納入個人意外保險","createTime":"2021-03-10T04:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T07:39:33.000Z","uid":261647,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6988413114152a0f7b016650008f3b24b23f5ae1","tid":2440510,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:15:05.000Z","msg":"https://hk. appledaily. com/local/20210309/I3KXUHU3HZH45EREGWT2V5IYQQ/<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HGOG6HVDH5DHZOTZ3GZJIWC5UY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHGOG6HVDH5DHZOTZ3GZJIWC5UY.png&h=c6667cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港上月底開展接種武漢肺炎疫苗計劃，至今發生至少5宗嚴重異常事件，其中3人死亡，2人需接受深切治療，另有多人不適送院。部份個案經專家委員會初步檢視後，認為與接種疫苗沒有直接關係，能否獲政府疫苗保障基金補償仍存疑問。<br />\n<br />\n有保險業人士指出，若接種疫苗後出現嚴重病況或不幸逝世，不會納入個人意外保險保障，「因為你明知去打針（接種），有個風險喺度，而唔係不可預料之事（unforeseeable）」。"},{"pid":"97288a1f4d30b6886a70a8a49d7583663c95feec","tid":2440510,"uid":111253,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"出街我都明知有風險俾車撞喎"},{"pid":"fa15593bd3e381b8b836549d9885253f366f7db9","tid":2440510,"uid":57677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OsY5O1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOsY5O1W.jpg&h=b45a1235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DysN2nc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDysN2nc.jpg&h=41e374d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9475dcdb50500a649b27b8a8ea4860c51a7d5181","tid":2440510,"uid":92783,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"搭飛機都有風險，買咗保險係咪冇得賠？<br />\n冇風險使撚買你啲保險咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234e1b260732ef19466f6fde6676ecafac3ab19b","tid